{"type":"message","id":"324013d8","parentId":"5c54fb16","timestamp":"2026-05-15T03:53:27.870Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the issue. After the \"Git拉新\" step completed at 11:52:51, there was a log message:\n\n```\n-----Jump out the build step-----\n```\n\nAnd then:\n```\nBatchmode quit successfully invoked - shutting down!\n```\n\nThe `-----Jump out the build step-----` message followed by the shutdown suggests the pipeline decided to skip or jump out of the remaining build steps. This might be a condition in the pipeline code that checks something and decides not to proceed.\n\nBut wait, I should check whether the pipeline actually completed all its steps. Let me look at the pipeline configuration. The keyword \"Jump out the build step\" suggests it intentionally skipped the remaining steps. This could be by design (e.g., if there are no asset changes, it might skip the resource build step).\n\nActually, looking at the code reference:\n```\nYYZY.BuildPipeline.BuildPipeline:ExecuteContinued () (at Assets/Editor/BuildPipeline/BuildPipeline.cs:222)\n```\n\nLine 222 is where \"Jump out the build step\" is logged. This sounds like it's part of the normal pipeline flow - perhaps it finished the pipeline and the remaining steps are not relevant.\n\nThe pipeline still needs to do:\n1. ✅ Git拉新 - DONE (5.36s)\n2. ❓ 打包资源 (build resources)\n3. ❓ 上传CDN (upload to CDN)\n4. ❓ 其他步骤\n\nBut it jumped out. Let me look at whether the pipeline configuration might have been set up correctly.\n\nHmm, actually, wait. Let me re-examine the full log. I see the pipeline ran step \"Git拉新\" and after it completed, it says \"Jump out the build step\" and then quit. This could mean:\n\n1. The pipeline was configured to only have the \"Git拉新\" step for batch mode\n2. Or there's a condition check that caused it to skip remaining steps\n3. Or perhaps the pipeline configuration needs additional setup in the EditorConfig\n\nThe task mentions: \"首次使用需在 Unity Editor 中打开 BuildPipeline 窗口配置好 '热更' 流水线的各步骤参数\"\n\nSo it's possible the pipeline configuration is incomplete. But since Unity exited with return code 0 successfully, technically the pipeline did run through its configured steps.\n\nLet me check if there are resource building or CDN upload artifacts. Also, let me look at the bat file to understand what it does.\n\nActually, I think the pipeline might have only executed the steps that are configured for batch mode. And the \"热更\" pipeline might have been configured with just the \"Git拉新\" step in the BuildPipeline window.\n\nLet me check if there is any additional information about what steps are in the pipeline.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我检查一下流水线是否只配置了「Git拉新」步骤，以及其他步骤是否已配置。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_2TLZGc1NFEN3zuKCWpTD2503","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-Content \"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log\" -TotalCount 1000 | Select-String -Pattern \"(Updating|Jump out|Batchmode quit)\" -Context 0,2","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":8727,"output":708,"cacheRead":20608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30043,"cost":{"input":0.00122178,"output":0.00019824000000000003,"cacheRead":0.000577024,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001997044}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778817199685,"responseId":"264f0c16-dba8-4a2c-9be7-1b82e402de8e"}}
