{"type":"message","id":"2edd8d5d","parentId":"0eeaa90f","timestamp":"2026-05-15T03:57:11.220Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The log doesn't have the \"Exiting batchmode successfully now!\" message, which is a bit concerning. But it's showing the shutdown sequence (cleanup mono, disconnected). The bat file's Unity process ended without the typical success message. Let me check the bat process exit code.\n\nActually, looking at the bat session, let me check if it has exited and what the exit code was.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Vyeczwcc2t8kZHEriwY75129","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"poll","sessionId":"gentle-cove","timeout":5000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":416,"output":161,"cacheRead":63872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64449,"cost":{"input":0.000058240000000000005,"output":0.00004508,"cacheRead":0.001788416,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001891736}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778817428992,"responseId":"99f64690-1410-4c06-8667-f72a3c9af7c9"}}
