{"type":"message","id":"9d9ed551","parentId":"cc610a02","timestamp":"2026-05-15T03:57:34.018Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There was a critical error during the asset bundle build! \n\nThe error is:\n```\nSystem.Exception: 存在差异资源包！请查看警告信息！\n```\n\nThis is from YooAsset's `TaskVerifyBuildResult` which checks that the built asset bundles match what was expected. It says \"存在差异资源包\" which means there are resource package differences.\n\nAlso, there's a 404 error:\n```\nSystem.Net.WebException: The remote server returned an error: (404) Not Found.\n```\n\nThis might be from a CDN check or version check step.\n\nSo the pipeline partially ran but the asset bundle build FAILED. The pipeline ran through:\n1. ✅ Git拉新 - success\n2. ✅ HybridCLR DLL compilation - success (\"BuildPlayerGenerator: Succeeded\" appeared multiple times)\n3. ❌ YooAsset resource build - FAILED with \"存在差异资源包！请查看警告信息！\"\n\nThis means the test server update was NOT successful. I need to report this failure back to the main agent.\n\nLet me also check if the CDN upload step was reached. Given the build failure, it likely wasn't reached.\n\nLet me also check for the \"Jump out\" message in the second run to see if it also got interrupted by compilation.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"流水线执行失败！YooAsset 打包阶段出现错误。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ZeNZFJUR3nCfiUTsRb242869","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-Content \"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log\" | Select-String -Pattern \"存在差异|构建失败|Jump out|Quit\" -Context 0,3","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":14713,"output":386,"cacheRead":65536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80635,"cost":{"input":0.00205982,"output":0.00010808000000000001,"cacheRead":0.001835008,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0040029079999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778817449076,"responseId":"