{"type":"message","id":"343f1b38","parentId":"9d9ed551","timestamp":"2026-05-15T03:57:38.258Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_ZeNZFJUR3nCfiUTsRb242869","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"> -quit\r\n  -nographics\r\n  -projectPath\r\n  E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":4211,"aggregated":"> -quit\r\n  -nographics\r\n  -projectPath\r\n  E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778817458258}}
{"type":"message","id":"832678d0","parentId":"343f1b38","timestamp":"2026-05-15T03:57:45.778Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting - only the startup \"-quit\" line matched, and there's no \"Jump out\" or \"Quit\" in the second run. The `存在差异` line I saw earlier didn't match because of encoding issues.\n\nThe pipeline had a build failure with the YooAsset verification. The error message is clear: \"存在差异资源包！请查看警告信息！\" - there are resource package differences, meaning the generated asset bundles don't match what YooAsset expects.\n\nThis is likely a resource mismatch issue. Let me check what the warnings/errors looked like more specifically.\n\nThe pipeline execution summary:\n1. First run (PID 3920): ✅ Git拉新 (5.36s) - pulled new code, but was interrupted by script compilation\n2. Second run (PID 21872): Started from suspended state, executed remaining steps:\n   - ✅ Lua compilation (many files compiled)\n   - ✅ HybridCLR DLL compilation (BuildPlayerGenerator: Succeeded appeared many times)\n   - ❌ YooAsset AssetBundle build failed: \"存在差异资源包！请查看警告信息！\" (there are resource package differences)\n\nThe build failure means the test server update is NOT complete. I need to report this to the main agent and also notify in the Feishu group about the failure.\n\nActually wait - I need to check if this error happened before or after the CDN upload, and how the pipeline handled it. Looking at the error more carefully:\n\n```\nSystem.Exception: 存在差异资源包！请查看警告信息！\nat YooAsset.Editor.TaskVerifyBuildResult.VerifyingBuildingResult (...)\nat YooAsset.Editor.AssetBundleBuilder.Run (...)\nat YooAssetBuildForPipeline:BuildForPipeline (...)\nat YYZY.BuildPipeline.BuildPipelineMethod:PipelineCreateBundle (...)\nat YYZY.BuildPipeline.BuildPipelineMethod:PipelineBuildAssetBundle (...)\n```\n\nSo the YooAsset build failed at the verification stage. The build attempted to build asset bundles for multiple targets:\n1. First attempt failed\n2. Second attempt also failed with the same error\n\nAnd then there was a 404 error for a web request.\n\nThe pipeline didn't reach the CDN upload step because the asset bundle build failed.\n\nI should report this to the main agent with the failure details. The main agent can then decide what to do.\n\nLet me also check the exit code and the very end of the log one more time.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_LDE0dqCfyiTt9fBQxE3R9666","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-Content \"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log\" -Tail 50 | Select-Object -First 30","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":167,"output":608,"cacheRead":80512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81287,"cost":{"input":0.000023380000000000003,"output":0.00017024000000000002,"cacheRead":0.002254336,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0024479560000000003}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778817458262,"responseId":"0dae8f0d-694e-450f-a69e-daa896b62cf7"}}
