{"type":"message","id":"b816d235","parentId":"80b14c57","timestamp":"2026-05-15T03:57:52.335Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The log ends with Unity shutting down - the last significant messages are:\n1. Performance data (Application.Shutdown)\n2. Asset import\n3. RefreshProfile with large PostProcessAllAssets (4.07 seconds)\n\nBut I notice there's no \"Exiting batchmode\" or \"Succeeded\" message. The \"Application.Shutdown.SaveSceneManagerSetup\" line indicates Unity is shutting down. It seems like the pipeline threw an exception (from the build failure) and Unity exited with an error code.\n\nGiven this situation, I need to:\n1. Report the failure to the main session agent\n2. The CDN upload step was NOT reached, so the test server is NOT updated\n\nLet me report back to the main session.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"任务执行完毕。总结我的发现：\n\n## 执行结果总结\n\n**总体状态：❌ 部分失败**\n\n### 流水线执行详情\n\n**第1次运行（PID 3920）：**\n- ✅ Git拉新 - 成功（5.36s），拉取了新代码 `2946c94..89c735c`\n- ⏭️ 因 Git 更新了 `Effect_510.cs` 触发脚本重新编译，流水线被中断（`Jump out the build step`）\n- 后续步骤（打包资源、上传CDN）未执行\n\n**第2次运行（PID 21872）——从挂起状态恢复：**\n- ✅ Lua 脚本编译 - 成功（大量 Lua 文件编译通过）\n- ✅ HybridCLR DLL 编译 - 成功（`BuildPlayerGenerator: Succeeded`）\n- ❌ **YooAsset AssetBundle 打包失败**\n  - 错误：`存在差异资源包！请查看警告信息！`\n  - 来源：`TaskVerifyBuildResult.VerifyingBuildingResult`\n  - 同一个错误重复出现两次（可能对两个平台）\n- ⏭️ CDN 上传步骤未到达\n\n### 结论\n测试服更新**未完成**。AssetBundle 资源打包阶段验证失败，导致流水线中断。需要主人检查 YooAsset 配置中的资源差异问题后重新执行。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":693,"output":445,"cacheRead":81280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82418,"cost":{"input":0.00009702,"output":0.00012460000000000002,"cacheRead":0.00227584,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00249746}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778817466607,"responseId":"dfac4730-930a-488d-b93e-0a11b20e93d5"}}
